<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Mission to Io</title>
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="10">
    <style>
        body { 
            background-color: #1a0a00; /* Dark Volcanic Rock */
            color: #ffcc00; 
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            text-align: center;
            border: 20px solid #e65100; /* Thick Lava Border */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
        }
        h1 { 
            font-size: 5em; 
            color: #ff3d00; 
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 4px 4px #5d1c00, 0 0 20px #ff3d00;
        }
        .mission-info {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            color: #ffb18a;
            line-height: 1.6;
            border-bottom: 3px double #ff3d00;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .dashboard {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .temp-display {
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #ff3d00, #8d2400);
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 10px solid #ffcc00;
            box-shadow: 0 0 50px #ff3d00;
        }
        .temp-val { font-size: 4em; font-weight: bold; color: white; }
        .label { font-size: 1.5em; color: #ffcc00; letter-spacing: 3px; font-weight: bold;}
        
        .camera-feed img {
            width: 550px;
            border: 8px solid #ffcc00;
            box-shadow: 15px 15px 0px #5d1c00;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .status-bar {
            margin-top: 50px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            background: #ff3d00;
            color: #1a0a00;
            padding: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Mission to Io</h1>
    
    <div class="mission-info">
        <strong>OBJECTIVE:</strong> Galaxy Explorers Probe #1 is currently deployed to the surface of Io, 
        Jupiter's most volcanic moon. We are monitoring extreme heat signatures and capturing 
        visual data to locate active sulfur volcanoes and lava lakes.
    </div>

    <div class="dashboard">
        <div class="temp-display">
            <div class="label">HEAT LEVEL</div>
            <div class="temp-val">{{ temp }}°C</div>
        </div>

        <div class="camera-feed">
            <div class="label">LIVE SURFACE FEED</div>
            <img src="{{ url_for('static', filename='io_image.jpg') }}?random=1" alt="Io Surface Photo">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="status-bar">
        PROBE STATUS: ACTIVE & TRANSMITTING | SCANNING FOR MAGMA
    </div>

</body>
</html>